Sakura Monitoring

This repository contains a maintained Sakura frontend theme integrated with
source from the Nezha dashboard and nezha-dash-v2 projects.

Nezha dashboard:
  https://github.com/nezhahq/nezha

nezha-dash-v2:
  https://github.com/hamster1963/nezha-dash-v2

The upstream source directories retain their original Apache License 2.0
license files. Upstream commit pins are recorded in upstreams.lock.json.

ISO TopoJSON:
  https://github.com/rembish/iso-topojson
  Version 1.4.0, licensed under CC BY 4.0. The country and territory
  geometries are derived from the public-domain Natural Earth 10m dataset.

Komari loading animation reference:
  https://komari.mikus.ink/
  https://komari.mikus.ink/assets/img/loli.gif
  The default loading animation is a local copy of the referenced asset and
  can be replaced or disabled through window.CustomLoadingIllustration.
